description: Removes entire attributes (key and value pairs) from the findings that are specified by the ARNs of the findings where an attribute with the specified key exists.

parameters.name: findingArns
parameters.description: The ARNs that specify the findings that you want to remove attributes from. (string) ---

parameters.name: attributeKeys
parameters.description: The array of attribute keys that you want to remove from specified findings. (string) ---

nested_items.name: failedItems
nested_items.description: Attributes details that cannot be described. An error code is provided for each failed item.

nested_items.name: failureCode
nested_items.description: The status code of a failed item.

nested_items.name: retryable
nested_items.description: Indicates whether you can immediately retry a request for this item for a specified resource.
